org.sbml.jsbml
Class CVTerm

java.lang.Object
  org.sbml.jsbml.AbstractTreeNode
      org.sbml.jsbml.AnnotationElement
          org.sbml.jsbml.CVTerm
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, TreeNode, TreeNodeWithChangeSupport
public class CVTerm
extends AnnotationElement

Contains all the MIRIAM URIs for a MIRIAM qualifier in the annotation element of a SBML component.

Since:
0.8
Version:
$Rev: 1358 $
Author:

CVTerm

public CVTerm()
Creates a CVTerm instance. By default, the type and qualifier of this CVTerm are null. The list of resourceURIS is empty.

filterResources

public List<String> filterResources(String pattern)
Returns a list of resources that contain the given pattern. This is useful to obtain, e.g., all KEGG resources this term points to.

Parameters:
pattern - e.g., "urn:miriam:kegg.reaction:R" or just "kegg".
Returns:
A list of all resources that contain the given pattern. This list can be empty.
